    <item>
      <title>议员称税务官未能解决数十亿英镑的欺诈行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/taxman-failing-to-tackle-billions-of-pounds-of-fraud-mps-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[议员们表示，英国税务机关可能严重低估了非法避税行为，且没有采取足够措施来解决这一问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/taxman-failing-to-tackle-billions-of-pounds-of-fraud-mps-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普顾问称澳大利亚正在“扼杀”美国铝市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/australia-is-killing-us-aluminum-market-trump-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的高级贸易顾问表示，澳大利亚正在“扼杀”美国铝市场，这可能会对澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯争取下个月生效的关税豁免的努力造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/australia-is-killing-us-aluminum-market-trump-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫禁止记者参加“美国湾”争端活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/white-house-bars-reporter-from-event-in-gulf-of-america-flap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，白宫禁止美联社记者报道总统唐纳德·特朗普和顾问埃隆·马斯克的活动，这家长期通讯社表示，此举是对其风格指南未采用总统新的“美国湾”标签的惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/white-house-bars-reporter-from-event-in-gulf-of-america-flap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:10:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
