    <item>
      <title>司法部的亚当斯令暗示与华尔街检察官的对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/doj-adams-order-cues-showdown-with-wall-street-prosecutors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普司法部下令曼哈顿联邦检察官撤销对纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯的腐败案件，此举为监管华尔街的政府律师的独立性埋下了伏笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/doj-adams-order-cues-showdown-with-wall-street-prosecutors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 22:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赖特称美国应停止关闭燃煤电厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/us-should-stop-closure-of-coal-fired-power-plants-wright-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源部长克里斯·赖特表示，美国应该停止关闭燃煤发电厂，并补充说，未来几十年，燃煤燃料来源对国家电力系统至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/us-should-stop-closure-of-coal-fired-power-plants-wright-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 21:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
